<p>The Masked Singer has hit Australian TV screens but if you're still unsure about the concept then why not pay more attention to Dannii Minogue's wardrobe like we are at Fashion Finder HQ.</p>

<p>The judge got dressed up for another show in this gorgeous bespoke dress by Australian couture label couture+love+madness. Stylist Rachel Dennis completed the look with Steve Madden heels and jewellery by Shannakian.</p>

<p>We're loving the disco-inspired sparkle, the ruched silhouette that flatters the figure and statement off-shoulder bodice, it's perfect for such a glitzy event.</p>

