<p>The singer's look even inspired a few fans to consider adopting some rosy locks of their own. </p>

<p>One person Tweeted: 'Oh my god Minogue. You look stunning!!!! Ahh I want my pink hair back.' </p>

<p>Several fans compared her to the show's masked Kitten character, who has pink fur. </p>

<p>One pink hair enthusiast wrote: 'Christ, Dannii with pink hair!!!! That is A LOOK. Killing it'</p>

<p>Someone wrote: 'Cute Kitty!!! Pink is my fave hair colour on you,' while others suggested she wore the pink look to match the Kitten. </p>

<p>Sadly for fans of the disco-inspired look, Dannii admitted in a Twitter post that the hair is a wig. </p>

<p>Quoting Dolly Parton, she wrote: 'People always ask me how long it takes to do my hair. I don't know, I'm never there.'</p>

